      "callsToAction": [],
      "text": "BEYOND ONE-SHOT GENERATION Research. Plan. Build. Own. Squid Agent brings current web knowledge and a deliberate planning workflow into the same pipeline that generates, checks, and exports your React application. INPUT Start with an idea, screenshot, or website. Describe a product in plain language, upload a visual reference, or point Squid Agent at an existing site. It carries that context through the build instead of reducing your request to a one-shot mockup. RESEARCH Build with current docs, APIs, and facts. When a request depends on external knowledge, Squid Agent can search the live web",
